          <p><inline-formula><mml:math id="me80"><mml:mrow><mml:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><mml:mi>G</mml:mi></mml:mstyle><mml:mn>2</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:math></inline-formula>: Only diploid SNPs were used, and genotypes were known without error. <inline-formula><mml:math id="me81"><mml:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><mml:mi>M</mml:mi></mml:mstyle></mml:math></inline-formula> (<xref ref-type="disp-formula" rid="eq1">Equation 1</xref>) has elements ranging between 0 and 2.</p>
